<text>
<body>
<head>POEM</head>

<lg type="tercet" n="1"><l n="1">Wouldn’t it be funny</l>
<l n="2">if The Finger had designed us</l>
<l n="3">to shit just once a week?</l></lg>

<l n="4">all week long we’d get fatter</l>
<l n="5">and fatter and then on Sunday morning</l>
<l n="6">while everyone’s in church</l>
<l n="7">ploop!</l>
</body>
<date>1959</date>
</text>